            . My husband's name is Thomas. I missed these things on the 8th of October.</p>
               <p>Q. What is the prisoner - A. She came to see me. I gave her a cup of tea, and when my back was turned I lost my property. I found the apron at Mr. Barker's, in the Commercial-road. The shirt was brought to me to be washed on the Monday morning.</p>
               <p>
            
